# OpenBB Logo Placeholder

This file serves as a placeholder for the OpenBB logo that should be included in the DXT package.

For the actual DXT package, you should replace this with a proper PNG image file (openbb-logo.png) that represents the OpenBB brand.

The logo should be:
- PNG format
- Square aspect ratio (recommended: 256x256 pixels)
- Transparent background
- OpenBB branding compliant

The logo will be displayed in MCP clients when showing the extension information.